<paragraph pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Holotype: BMNH 1848.10.4.6 (additional numbers Dh.2, 252), West Africa, coll. Rev. Allen; label text, presumably by Carter, reads Trikentrion Ehlers, very long acuates.</paragraph>
